类 ModifiedASMAnalyzer

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.flink.shaded.asm5.org.objectweb.asm.Opcodes

    @Internal
public class ModifiedASMAnalyzer
extends org.apache.flink.shaded.asm5.org.objectweb.asm.tree.analysis.Analyzer
    Modified version of ASMs Analyzer. It defines a custom ASM Frame and allows jump modification which is necessary for UDFs with one iterable input e.g. GroupReduce. (see also UdfAnalyzer's field "iteratorTrueAssumptionApplied")
